1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:03,930
The Hallerbos forest is near in Brussels, Belgium.

2
00:00:04,890 --> 00:00:06,600
It is very famous.

3
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:11,100
Thousands of people visit the forest every spring.

4
00:00:11,910 --> 00:00:13,500
They want to see bluebells.

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,320
A bluebell  is a small plant.

6
00:00:17,310 --> 00:00:19,440
It often grows in forests.

7
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:22,440
It blooms in the middle of April.

8
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:25,130
It's flowers are blue.

9
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:28,650
Many bluebells are in holler boss.

10
00:00:29,340 --> 00:00:31,560
It looks like a blue carpet.

11
00:00:32,549 --> 00:00:35,700
Sequoia trees are in the forest, too.

12
00:00:36,780 --> 00:00:40,410
Authorities close the parking lots near the forest.

13
00:00:41,190 --> 00:00:42,420
They cancel buses.

14
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,879
They say that it is better.

15
00:00:44,910 --> 00:00:49,440
If people stay at home, some people still come.

16
00:00:50,370 --> 00:00:53,190
They say that they feel good in nature.

17
00:00:54,705 --> 00:00:58,735
Restaurants and bars closed because of the Coronavirus.

18
00:00:59,775 --> 00:01:02,235
People cannot go to many places.

19
00:01:03,345 --> 00:01:08,775
It is still important to go outside and spend time in nature.

